data.description:
Wow! This 1886 Carondelet home is ready for its new owners! Let's see if this one checks the boxes? 
Original Hardwood Floors
3 Bedrooms
2 Full Bathrooms
10 ft Pocket Doors
10 Ft Front Door
11 ft Ceilings on the first floor
All brick home
Tons of Natural Light
Private Deck off of the Master Bedroom
Rear Access Off Street Parking
Dual Zoned HVAC
Deck off of Kitchen over looking backyard - Perfect for breakfast coffee or entertaining family and friends.
Minutes from I-55
Last but not least 2,000 sf of home under $250,000 very hard to find move in ready. 

Don't wait to schedule your tour, you need to see this one if you're looking for old world charm and spacious living!
